notes: Namibia: 50 runs in 6.6 overs (44 balls), Extras 8
3rd Wicket: 50 runs in 33 balls (N Davin 30, MG Erasmus 15, Ex 7)
Namibia: 100 runs in 14.4 overs (90 balls), Extras 8

milestones.description: Assad Vala and Charles Amini's 153-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 98 between Mahuru Dai and Sese Bau
Erasmus and Davin's 147-run partnership is NAM's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 124 between Erasmus and JP Kotze
This is the highest match aggregate (714) involving teams P.N.G. & Namibia in ODIs
Assad Vala and Charles Amini's 153-run partnership is PNG's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 146 between Kiplin Doriga and Tony Ura
Charles Amini has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (80) in an innings in ODIs for PNG, going past Tony Ura's 76
Erasmus has broken the record for most sixes (34) in ODIs for NAM, going past JJ Smit's 31
Charles Amini has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (8) in ODIs for PNG, going past Tony Ura's 6
